<a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>", "commentRss"=>"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-sports-and-competition/feed/"}, {"title"=>"Year in Pictures: Conflict and protests", "link"=>"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-war-and-conflict/", "comments"=>["http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-war-and-conflict/#comments", "0"], "pubDate"=>"Sun, 21 Dec 2014 16:47:30 +0000", "creator"=>"Andrew Tolson", "category"=>["Photo", "Best of 2014"], "guid"=>{"__content__"=>"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=655875", "isPermaLink"=>"false"}, "description"=>"<p>The best snaps of global conflict and protests from our Week in Pictures series</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-war-and-conflict/\">Year in Pictures: Conflict and protests</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>", "encoded"=>"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><p>Every week, our photo editors curate the <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/week-in-pictures\" target=\"_blank\">Week in Pictures series</a>, a collection of some of the most stunning, moving, vivid, adorable and heartbreaking photos from the last seven days. As part of our <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/best-of-2014\" target=\"_blank\">Best of 2014 web series</a>, we&#8217;ve assembled galleries of some of the best snaps we&#8217;ve found. Here&#8217;s the most remarkable photos from a year of global upheaval:</p>\n<script type='text/javascript'>var image_max_height = \"500\";</script><script type='text/javascript'>var imagesArray = [{\"id\":653867,\"mlpId\":\"5787\",\"src\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/458441228-copy-660x440.jpg\",\"width\":660,\"height\":440,\"medSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/458441228-copy-150x150.jpg\",\"medWidth\":150,\"medHeight\":150,\"smallSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp